(3, 479, 2,'Yamaha Rydeen 5-Piece Shell Pack With 22\" Bass Drum - Champagne Glitter', 'Yamaha Rydeen 5-piece shell pack was designed to inspire young drummers with quality sound. This shell pack utilizes genuine Yamaha tom holders for simple adjustments and features solid and glitter finishes. Yamaha Hardware allows creative setup variations and grows with the needs of a younger player. Rydeen quality will ensure your young drummer spends more time playing and less time tuning or adjusting less expensive alternatives.  Cymbals and hardware are not included.'),
(3, 284, 2, 'Simmons Titan 20 Electronic Drum Kit With Mesh Pads & Bluetooth', 'The Simmons Titan 20 electronic drum kit delivers an immersive and customizable playing experience for drummers of all levels. Featuring Bluetooth MIDI connectivity and a robust drum module, this kit offers seamless integration with the Simmons app to tailor sounds to your exact preferences. With a library of professionally recorded drum samples, the Titan 20 allows players to play along with their favorite songs or create custom kits. Its high-quality mesh pads provide a responsive and natural feel, while its durable four-post rack ensures consistent performance. Whether for practice, jamming, or recording, the Titan 20 stands out with its blend of advanced technology and thoughtful design. Built-in Bluetooth audio streaming further enhances its versatility, making it an interactive solution for today\'s drummers.'),
(2, 1999, 2, 'Roland TD316 V-Drums Electronic Drum Set', 'Small in footprint but big in terms of stage energy, the Roland TD316 V-Drums kit packs expressive playability and pro features into a compact setup built for real drummers. Driven by the V31 sound module—the same advanced sound engine found in Roland’s top-tier V71—it delivers authentic tone, lifelike response and endless room to grow. Dual crash cymbals expand creative fills, while the PD-12P snare with triple sensors and positional sensing mirrors the feel of an acoustic drum. With Bluetooth audio, DAW integration and wireless app control, the TD316 bridges home practice, studio recording and live performance. It all equates to an electronic kit that represents next step in Roland’s legacy of combining innovation with the feel and soul of real drums.'),
(0, 449, 2, 'Yamaha Rydeen 5-Piece Shell Pack With 22" Bass Drum - Black Glitter', 'Yamaha Rydeen 5-piece shell pack was designed to inspire young drummers with quality sound. This shell pack utilizes genuine Yamaha tom holders for simple adjustments and features solid and glitter finishes. Yamaha Hardware allows creative setup variations and grows with the needs of a younger player. Rydeen quality will ensure your young drummer spends more time playing and less time tuning or adjusting less expensive alternatives. \nCymbals and hardware are not included')
